{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.400", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einen sch\u00f6nen guten Abend, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.400", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.120", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.400", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen \u00fcber unseren Antrag heute abstimmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.520", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir werden dar\u00fcber heute auch abstimmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.560", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil wir dazu beschlussf\u00e4hig sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.600", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Rassismus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.840", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Rechtsextremismus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.200", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Antisemitismus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.040", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diskriminierung jeglicher Art und antidemokratische Hetze d\u00fcrfen in unserem Land an keiner Stelle in unserer Gesellschaft einen Platz haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.840", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Menschenfeindlichkeit und rechte Hetze sind aber leider trotzdem traurige, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.600", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bittere und erschreckende Realit\u00e4t\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.640", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "seit der letzten Wahl leider auch in diesem Parlament."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.880", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sehen dem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.440", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.400", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber nicht tatenlos zu."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.720", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das haben wir heute Morgen bereits in der Debatte zum 70-j\u00e4hrigen Jubil\u00e4um des Staates Israel gesagt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.720", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sehen bei Antisemitismus nicht tatenlos zu, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.720", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir sehen bei rechtsextremer Hetze nicht tatenlos zu."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.880", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben aus unserer Geschichte gelernt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.800", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.560", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir eine wehrhafte Demokratie brauchen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.600", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Demokratie und Rechtsstaat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.360", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Schutz der Menschenw\u00fcrde\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.400", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das sehen wir in vielen L\u00e4ndern Europas und in anderen Teilen der Welt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.920", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind leider nicht selbstverst\u00e4ndlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.880", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern m\u00fcssen immer wieder und ganz konsequent von allen Demokratinnen und Demokraten verteidigt werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.960", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich sage allen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.640", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die skeptisch bei der Frage des Parteienverbots oder der Beschr\u00e4nkung von Rechten der Parteien sind: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.800", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Selbstverst\u00e4ndlich geh\u00f6ren demokratische Parteien zu einer guten Demokratie und einem Rechtsstaat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.080", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.520", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sie sind Voraussetzung f\u00fcr Parlamentarismus und f\u00fcr ganz gezielte und geordnete Interessenvertretung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.280", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen gibt es zu Recht den Artikel\u00a021 in unserem Grundgesetz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.160", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen gibt es zu Recht hohe H\u00fcrden f\u00fcr ein Parteiverbot. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.360", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr die SPD sage ich aber ganz deutlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.080", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir nach wie vor ein Verbot der NPD f\u00fcr richtig halten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.000", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es war gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.760", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Bundesrat den Antrag beim Bundesverfassungsgericht gestellt hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.320", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Bundesverfassungsgericht hat am 17.\u00a0Januar 2017 ganz klar festgestellt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.720", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die NPD verfassungsfeindliche Ziele verfolgt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.520", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die NPD wurde leider nur mangels Gef\u00e4hrlichkeit nicht verboten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.880", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man kann viel dar\u00fcber diskutieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.400", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie gef\u00e4hrlich eine Partei ist und wann der richtige Zeitpunkt f\u00fcr ein Verbot ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.120", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber unabh\u00e4ngig davon hat uns, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.160", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dem Gesetzgeber, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.720", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Bundesverfassungsgericht einen ganz wichtigen Hinweis gegeben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.400", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich dass wir gleichwohl jenseits eines Verbots, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.040", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unterhalb eines Verbots, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.920", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sanktionen vornehmen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.960", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben diese Sanktionsm\u00f6glichkeiten er\u00f6ffnet; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.240", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn es ist absolut unverst\u00e4ndlich\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.720", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "darauf haben wir uns hier im Bundestag verst\u00e4ndigt\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.480", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass verfassungsfeindliche Parteien staatliches Geld bekommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.120", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Harbarth hat zu Recht gesagt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.200", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei kommt es gar nicht auf die H\u00f6he an; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.080", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn jeder Cent f\u00fcr eine verfassungsfeindliche Partei aus staatlichen Mitteln ist einer zu viel."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.640", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben hier im Juli 2017 den Artikel\u00a021 Grundgesetz entsprechend ge\u00e4ndert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.960", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir haben das Parteiengesetz angepasst. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.840", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bundestag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.640", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bundesrat und Bundesregierung k\u00f6nnen jetzt einen Antrag stellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.720", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die staatliche Parteienfinanzierung ausgeschlossen wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.360", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Bundesrat hat das am 2.\u00a0Februar 2018 getan. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.360", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesregierung ist ihm am 18.\u00a0April gefolgt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.280", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.440", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.760", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das heute hier im Deutschen Bundestag beschlie\u00dfen und einen entsprechenden Antrag beim Bundesverfassungsgericht stellen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.960", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bitte wirklich um Zustimmung zu diesem wichtigen Antrag als ein deutliches Signal aus dem Deutschen Bundestag und freue mich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.480", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn dieser Antrag hier eine breite Mehrheit bekommt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.080", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.960", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr die FDP-Fraktion hat das Wort der Kollege Dr.\u00a0Stefan Ruppert."
   ]
  }
 ]
}